类 ClassLoaderFiles

  • java.lang.Object

  • 所有已实现的接口:

    public class ClassLoaderFiles
extends Object
implements ClassLoaderFileRepository, Serializable
    ClassLoaderFileRepository that maintains a collection of ClassLoaderFile items grouped by source folders.
